---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

---

<Layout title="Plombier & Déboucheur 24/7" description="Aqua Débouchage Service: Votre expert en débouchage d'urgence et plomberie à Bruxelles. Intervention rapide garantie.">
  
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="badge">Urgence 24h/24 & 7j/7</div>
        <h1>Expert en <span class="highlight">Débouchage</span> et Plomberie à Bruxelles</h1>
        <p>Intervention rapide en moins de 30 minutes. Tarifs transparents et travail garanti pour tous vos problèmes de canalisations bouchées ou fuites d'eau.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="tel:+32000000000" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Appeler Maintenant</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">Demander un Devis</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-image-wrapper">
        <div class="blob-bg"></div>
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607472586893-edb57cbce4ea?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" alt="Plombier professionnel au travail" class="hero-img" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services-preview">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header text-center">
        <h2>Nos Services de <span class="highlight">Qualité</span></h2>
        <p>Des solutions professionnelles pour tous vos problèmes de plomberie</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🚽</div>
          <h3>Débouchage WC & Éviers</h3>
          <p>Intervention immédiate pour tout type de bouchon. Équipement professionnel pour un résultat durable.</p>
          <a href="/services" class="service-link">En savoir plus &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">📷</div>
          <h3>Inspection Caméra</h3>
          <p>Diagnostic précis de vos canalisations par inspection vidéo pour localiser les problèmes avec exactitude.</p>
          <a href="/services" class="service-link">En savoir plus &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🔧</div>
          <h3>Réparation Fuites</h3>
          <p>Recherche et réparation rapide de toutes vos fuites d'eau pour éviter les dégâts majeurs.</p>
          <a href="/services" class="service-link">En savoir plus &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="container features-container">
      <div class="features-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581094794329-c8112a89af12?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" alt="Camionnette de service plomberie" class="rounded-img" />
      </div>
      <div class="features-content">
        <h2>Pourquoi Choisir <span class="highlight">Aqua Débouchage</span> ?</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>
            <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Intervention Ultra Rapide</h4>
              <p>Nous sommes sur place en moins de 30 minutes à Bruxelles et ses environs.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="feature-icon">💶</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Tarifs Transparents</h4>
              <p>Pas de mauvaises surprises, un devis clair est établi avant toute intervention.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="feature-icon">🏆</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Travail Garanti</h4>
              <p>Tous nos techniciens sont qualifiés et notre travail est garanti à 100%.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(244, 247, 246, 0.8) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,1) 100%);
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .hero-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background-color: rgba(0, 168, 255, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 168, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .highlight::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 5px;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 8px;
    background-color: rgba(0, 168, 255, 0.3);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .btn-large {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .hero-image-wrapper {
    flex: 1;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .blob-bg {
    position: absolute;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-secondary) 100%);
    border-radius: 40% 60% 70% 30% / 40% 50% 60% 50%;
    animation: blob 8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    z-index: 0;
    opacity: 0.1;
  }

  @keyframes blob {
    0% { border-radius: 40% 60% 70% 30% / 40% 50% 60% 50%; }
    100% { border-radius: 60% 40% 30% 70% / 60% 30% 70% 40%; }
  }

  .hero-img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 500px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 20px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  /* Services Preview */
  .services-preview {
    background-color: white;
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 68, 204, 0.1);
    background: white;
  }

  .service-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .service-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-link {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    transition: gap 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service-link:hover {
    gap: 5px;
  }

  /* Features */
  .features {
    background-color: var(--color-background-alt);
  }

  .features-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .features-image, .features-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .rounded-img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .features-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    background: white;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .feature-list h4 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .feature-list p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .hero-container, .features-container {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
    }
    .hero p {
      margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    }
    .hero-actions {
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .feature-list li {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
